title: I’m THAT popular?!
body:
Installed some crafty stats Worpress plugin and now I’m seeing that my fresh site has more than 1000 pageviews in JUST ONE HOUR. OMG, I never knew I was so popular, Markable.in didn’t provide any stats.

What should I do with it now, if I don’t want to make money on it, huh? 1 zillion dollars question.
